Narrator: 06.06.1976 - England London  
A dark figure looms over the city, casting a long shadow. 
The air is thick with tension, and the streets are eerily quiet. 
A girl, no more than thirteen years old, presented with highly unusual symptoms.
Her mother appealed to the Catholic Church for help, and it was granted.
Father Andrew, an exorcist, goes forth to his next duty.
